_sText: Aim_ag_tyr4 ----------- 12 players Description: Another skill map set within a small arena with objects placed tactically forcing you to use skill to eliminate your enemies. This is a texture map. I advise you not to jump in the pit in the middle :) I made this map to my own design and I like the extra factor the pit is giving. Objective: Use the objects and environment to beat your enemies in gunfights. Pure skill will save you from getting that one headshot you didn't deserve. You also don't deserve to fall in teh pit.
